<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-04-25 21:11:01.316995</lastBuildDate><item><title>Fight the Power</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qEGNkxt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OtHv6H7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qEGNkxt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CapCap]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>TIL</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Nrfic68</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tOQhnLi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Nrfic68</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>To be fair it is one kind of tie!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Mdk7AhT</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NEIoro2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m the only teacher in my building who always wears a tie. Professional ties, Garcia ties, cartoon ties, old ties (as in 1970-80s hand-me-downs), funky ties, ugly ties,…and well, you get the picture. I own over 130 ties. Almost all of them given to me. I believe I’ve paid for four.

Well, there is one tie I wear that my students look for every day, a solid black tie. I only wear them on test days. The reasoning I tell my students a test is as professional as a Black Tie Affair. Whenever a student sees me with a black tie on and it is not for their class their eyes get big and ask panically, “DO WE HAVE A TEST?” I have now classically conditioned them to fear my ties.

As a side note, we have finals. I also dress up for that. I’ve gone to the GoodWill and got a tuxedo. So on finals I wear that and my students laugh at it.

TL;DR I wear black ties on test days and my kids are afraid of them now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YRY0xuc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Proof of my collection!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Mdk7AhT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Hotsauceman]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Being nice to people is free. There's so much hate on this earth. Gotta look after your fellow man</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4sc3IWf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iq6hWzF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4sc3IWf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Love it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dNsgMh0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YQK5Djh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TkUCcG7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qznm8yt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/19waJYA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/d9S80eC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gDxsD22.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/57yju8h.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hr4v0Ay.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wB57yFG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" sr